---
import Img1 from "../../assets/images/heat.png";
import Img2 from "../../assets/images/tools.png";
import Img3 from "../../assets/images/idea.png";
---
<section class="bg-blue-900 mx-[25vw] rounded-xl flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-semibold text-white p-4">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center p-4">
        <img src={Img1.src} alt="" class="w-20 rounded-full mr-4">
        <div>
            <h1 class="text-xl">Fuel consumption lower than most competition:</h1>
            <br>
            <p class="">Our plants use less fuel per ton of mix than most 
                competing plants, whether diesel, oil, gas, or any alternative fuel.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="p-4">    
        <h1 class="text-xl">This is primarily due, to the following advantages, among other factors:</h1>
        <br>
        <ul class="pl-4">
            <li class="list-disc">Fuel preheater</li>
            <li class="list-disc">'Total air' burner with variable power</li>
            <li class="list-disc">Drum insulation</li>
            <li class="list-disc">Drum sealed against cold air entry</li>
            <li class="list-disc">Drum flights with radiant heat capture</li>
            <li class="list-disc">Drum flights with high-efficiency veiling</li>
            <li class="list-disc">No need for a 'cold air window' </li>
            <li class="list-disc">Computerized regulation of the entire system</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center p-4">
        <div>
            <h1 class="text-xl">Durability and Minimal Maintenance:</h1>
            <br>
            <p class="">Designed and manufactured to the highest quality standards,
                 using American-certified steel and top-brand components.
                <br>
                Robust design to withstand harsh operating conditions and ensure long-term performance.
            </p>
        </div>
        <img src={Img2.src} alt="" class="w-20 rounded-full mr-4">
    </div>
    <div class="p-4">
        <ul class="pl-4">
            <li class="list-disc">Heavy duty design and materials.</li>
            <li class="list-disc">High quality electrostatic automotive paint (baked) in medium to 
                small size pieces, and high quality paint in big pieces.
            </li>
            <li class="list-disc">High corrosion-resistance, high adherence and long lasting color.</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <p>Operation cycle of 100% in highly contaminated environments</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center p-4">
        <img src={Img3.src} alt="" class="w-20 rounded-full mr-4">
        <div>
            <h1 class="text-xl">Technology and Control:</h1>
            <br>
            <p class="">Advanced monitoring systems for real-time performance tracking and diagnostics.
                <br>
                Fully integrated software for precise control of temperature, fuel, asphalt, aggregates,
                 RAP, adittional materials and the produced hot-mix.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>